==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Struma
<hw>Stru"ma</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L., a scrofulous
tumor.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>Scrofula.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A cushionlike swelling on any
organ; especially, that at the base of the capsule in many
mosses.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Strumatic</ent>⟦br⟧
